  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>

        <div rend="parallel">
          <p xml:id="AN170-kilavi">talaimakaḷ kāmamikka kaḻipaṭar kiḷaviyāṟ <app><lem>colliyatu</lem><rdg wit="#SS #VP">coṟṟatu</rdg></app>.</p>
          <p xml:lang="en">What SHE said with a word of great distress when passion intensified.</p>
        </div>
        <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="AN170">
        <l><anchor n="1"/>kāṉaluṅ kaḻaṟātu kaḻiyuṅ kūṟātu</l>
        <l>tēṉimir naṟumalarp puṉṉaiyu moḻiyā</l>
        <l>toruniṉ ṉallatu piṟitiyātu milaṉē</l>
        <l>yiruṅkaḻi malarnta kaṇpō ṉeytaṟ</l>
        <l>kamaḻitaḻ nāṟṟa mamiḻteṉa nacaii</l>
        <l>taṇṭā tūtiya vaṇṭiṉaṅ kaḷiciṟantu</l>
        <l>pa<supplied>ṟavai</supplied> taḷarun tuṟaivaṉai nīyē</l>
        <l>collal vēṇṭumā <supplied>lalava</supplied> palkāṟ</l>
        <l><supplied>kai</supplied>taiyam paṭuciṉai yevvamō ṭacāaṅ</l>
        <l>kaṭaṟciṟu kākkai kāmar peṭaiyoṭu</l>
        <l>kōṭṭumīṉ vaḻaṅkum vēṭṭamaṭi parappiṉ</l>
        <l>veḷḷiṟāk kaṉavu naḷḷeṉ yāmattu</l>
        <l>niṉṉuṟu viḻumaṅ kaḷaintō</l>
        <l>ṭaṉṉuṟu viḻuma nīntumō veṉavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>The seashore grove does not murmur, the backwaters do not talk, (1)</l>
        <l>and the Puṉṉai tree with fragrant blossoms humming with honey [bees] does not speak. (2)</l>
        <l>Apart from you alone I have no one else. (3)</l>
        <l>You who belongs to the man from the ghat, where the swarm of bees that had filled themselves</l>
        <l>with cool pollen relax [their] wings, delight excelling, (6f.)</l>
        <l>yearning, as for ambrosia, for the nectar from the fragrant petals (5)</l>
        <l>of the eye-like blue waterlilies that bloom in the dark backwaters, (4)</l>
        <l>you just must to speak [to him], crab: (8a-c)</l>
        <l>“She who removed the distress you had, (13)</l>
        <l>at deepest midnight, when along with [its] desired female the little crow of the sea</l>
        <l>that languishes with trouble on the sinking Kaitai branch, many times(?),</l>
        <l>dreams, as the hunt is slack, of white prawns</l>
        <l>from the expanse [of water] where swordfish roam, (8d-12)</l>
        <l>will she get over the distress she has?” (14)</l>
      </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
  </text>

